data.description: Tucked in the trees is a beautiful home. Recently updated with new kitchen, gorgeous soap stone counters and new flooring. It's the finishing touches that can make the difference.  This home has a new $20,000 boiler system heating is with water and baseboard heating, New Windows throughout with lifetime transferable warranty , New flooring, new kitchen, new paint. This 3 bedroom 2 bath has a wonderful open deck  off the kitchen...perfect for entertaining. Steps from the deck leads to an area for the campfire pit, here wildlife is so comfortable, they just meander through.  Loads of storage and downstairs perfect for an art studio, workshop or whatever you can think of. There is also an attached small potting shed / workshop What a great area just moments from the lake where you can paddle board, kayak, canoe and of course fish. Yes electric motors or paddle please, no gas engines. We're finally ready to show...the new floors are in and they are beautiful!
